From 5047147588168fe6b48477cde9ac9a9ea820085e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Patrick Barsanti <patrick.barsanti@amarulasolutions.com>
Date: Thu, 26 Mar 2026 15:23:56 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] dts: upstream: arm64: rockchip: Update axe-sbc dts to match
 schematic

This patch is aimed at matching the minimal dts for the Axelera axe-sbc
(antelao) board with its schematic and the kernel dts coding style.

It should be functionally identical to the previous version, while
aligning the regulators and other small details with the schematic.

Upstream-Status: Pending
Signed-off-by: Patrick Barsanti <patrick.barsanti@amarulasolutions.com>
---
